@EU_Commission @Europarl_EN @ecb @EUCouncil @AngelaMerkel_PL @EmmanuelMacron @DerSPIEGEL @Le_Figaro 
'TRUMP THREATENS 20% TARIFF ON EU CAR IMPORTS'
EUROPE, YOU'VE EVERY REASON TO HIT BACK WHERE IT HURTS DONALD, AMERICAN EXPORTS TO EU

@EU_Commission @internetthought Mandatory upload filters will most certainly lead to overblocking. The chilling effect this has is real.
Republishing at the mercy of some platform operator is not free speech.
This is censorship.

@EU_Commission @GattAllan If by "used" you mean "available", sure.
But imho they are widely known to be inefficient and it's quite common to read about "illegitimately" blocked accounts , without notice, that had to wait a few months before being "unblocked".
Do you have any data to back up your claim?
